234
00:26:28,660 --> 00:26:32,880
[SPEAKER_00] Dignem glavu, saturacija 100% tlak normalan.

235
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:34,599
[SPEAKER_00] Molim dalje.

236
00:26:34,599 --> 00:26:39,279
[SPEAKER_00] Kako dignem glavu, saturacija 100% tlak normalan.

237
00:26:39,279 --> 00:26:41,380
