246
00:27:10,920 --> 00:27:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] I samo molim.

247
00:27:14,019 --> 00:27:19,180
[SPEAKER_00] I onda negde oko 7 satik rekli meni,

248
00:27:19,180 --> 00:27:21,279
