255
00:27:38,079 --> 00:27:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže, ovo što je jučer bilo,

256
00:27:41,460 --> 00:27:43,059
[SPEAKER_00] to je čudo.

257
00:27:47,500 --> 00:27:50,339
[SPEAKER_00] Posle nekoliko dana,

258
00:27:50,339 --> 00:27:53,180
[SPEAKER_00] Marijin naglio poravak.

259
00:27:53,180 --> 00:27:57,319
[SPEAKER_00] Nas pozovu doktori,

260
00:27:57,319 --> 00:27:58,779
[SPEAKER_00] kaže on mene,

261
00:27:58,779 --> 00:28:01,819
[SPEAKER_00] niti mi znamo

262
00:28:01,819 --> 00:28:03,339
[SPEAKER_00] kad je njoj loše,

263
00:28:03,339 --> 00:28:04,460
[SPEAKER_00] zbog čega je loše,

264
00:28:04,460 --> 00:28:07,220
[SPEAKER_00] niti znamo kad je njoj dobro,

265
00:28:07,220 --> 00:28:08,759
[SPEAKER_00] recimo,

266
00:28:08,759 --> 00:28:10,680
[SPEAKER_00] zbog čega ide na dobro.

267
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:14,240
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, mi ovo u potpunosti ne razumijemo.

268
00:28:14,240 --> 00:28:17,819
[SPEAKER_00] I taj, jel,

269
